"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:01:48.000Z","msg":"跟你個咪正確渣法 <br />\n新式個d如果炒左咪外圈錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:41:39.000Z","msg":"但新式外圈過線去下個出口可以唔打燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e15d9e2b2880d145f157fed451bd1506a4c15b","tid":2315694,"uid":60109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:45:35.000Z","msg":"睇地下條線囉"},{"pid":"dbdb182fd5f32ce3f004cacbf42be91a066480ad","tid":2315694,"uid":168897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:52:49.000Z","msg":"搭單問, 如果唔熟路埋到迴旋處入口先知道要喺第三個出口出, 但當時喺左線, 咁應唔應該等冇車一入就 cut 入內圈?  定做外圈L 算? <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1635cb79ca641ec76c29e271eaf6755726dad893","tid":2315694,"uid":269954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1967ee5a444ea8bd56e53d2176dac4839f9cfbc","tid":2315694,"uid":4519,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"舊式永世外圈立於不敗之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內圈幾正確都好，上到庭都係你輸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:00:09.000Z","msg":"咁只係你習慣左行舊式，新舊式畫線只係將內外嘅不敗對調，新式你喺內圈鍾意兜足360 都唔會阻到其他人出，一樣係不敗。唔熟路想睇定啲嘅麻煩入去內圈兜到夠，唔好喺外圈阻住其他人出，呢個係新式畫法嘅 rationale"},{"pid":"32f20ae4be8f465e905b90d403b53f0c2bbdcc49","tid":2315694,"uid":34910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"正確行法係跟運輸署個指引<br />\n不過由於香港人揸車太西 行舊式的確會有好多人選擇做外圏撚"},{"pid":"d27fa6893e4713f5b02ed550ec82a4b3e22e613a","tid":2315694,"uid":378350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:14:43.000Z","msg":"係個垃圾政府唔將全部統一做新式啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7bbf564b5826c9b273cc1c02148e6a619c05f3","tid":2315694,"uid":19627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbdb182fd5f32ce3f004cacbf42be91a066480ad","tid":2315694,"uid":168897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:52:49.000Z","msg":"搭單問, 如果唔熟路埋到迴旋處入口先知道要喺第三個出口出, 但當時喺左線, 咁應唔應該等冇車一入就 cut 入內圈?  定做外圈L 算? <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:17:04.000Z","msg":"你入圈前選定左行車線 決定你行邊條線<br />\n唔會外圈cut入內圈 再出口時cut番出黎 <br />\n就你呢個情況 你咪係外圈撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果舊式計 入圈時行外圈 咪兜到第三個路口出 <br />\n新式既話 你每行一個出口都要打右燈 兼睇實隔籬線有冇車想出 因為係你cut線"},{"pid":"0751f98c7e7209b0f541826b10916a37910b4816","tid":2315694,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"第一二個出口 外圈<br />\n第三出口以上 內轉外圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce3fd5d6d9f9a35142247981ebbcde1da6e3d41","tid":2315694,"uid":77905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"外圈係大撚晒<br />\n<br />\n世界上好多嘢都係大撚晒<br />\n技安大撚晒唔同你又學佢咩<br />\n民建聯大撚晒又唔見你即刻入民建聯<br />\n<br />\n法例就係內圈撞外圈一撚定輸<br />\n因為你衰咗變換行車線前無留意交通狀況<br />\n乜嘢運輸署指引都係假 <br />\n佢叫你用內圈，無講嘅係炒車都係後果自負<br />\n<br />\n外圈係好撚巴閉<br />\n但另一方面只代表佢係車都唔識揸嘅撚樣<br />\n<br />\n外圈撚小心啲，正義終會申張<br />\n總有一日會換晒做新式螺旋形 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f04f3fb2a0417067ac1c135776793655199a598","tid":2315694,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e15d9e2b2880d145f157fed451bd1506a4c15b","tid":2315694,"uid":60109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:45:35.000Z","msg":"睇地下條線囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"無用，新式個隻可以唔打燈就過線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36aae89f7b9cbd215d375ba0e10fdf14494a9d15","tid":2315694,"uid":60109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f04f3fb2a0417067ac1c135776793655199a598","tid":2315694,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"