e":"2020-12-08T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"但係內圈唔打燈點知佢出圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除非每個出口停一停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"行自己條線點解要打燈"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cU8cOUa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcU8cOUa.png&h=5c1cdaa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 正路就算自己線都係要打架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"打係人情，唔打燈都唔會輸<br />\n咁我下次打啦"},{"pid":"d0b9b5919ea94d6ccb5997c3a643505cae3281d9","tid":2315694,"uid":122885,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"其實打足燈，有留意清楚隔離線有冇車平排，舊式迴旋處根本就唔恐怖。<br />\n如果外線有車頂到實咪兜多個圈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多人都係無睇清楚有冇其他車、以為夠快cut到先出事"},{"pid":"595448a4db563518ff793639f5ae02b60326b4f1","tid":2315694,"uid":36054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"兩線入圈 咪左一二右三四<br />\n第一 二出口 用左線入<br />\n三 四 出口用右線入<br />\n<br />\n我成日都記左一二右三四"}]}